quote>有d人係會驚另一半同異性行得太埋會做d太親密既行為<br />\n未必講到扑野咁嚴重 但係可能搣面之類都已經有d over左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話晒咁另一半知道會唔開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁親密就當然啦 但如果因爲驚呢啲親密行為<br />\n就要斷哂異性來往 未免治標唔治本喎"},{"pid":"d19d422f4da1946873cf6ce3d356f9d411715b76","tid":296460,"uid":80954,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"唔需要斷哂異性來往，但要識避忌，有容易引起懷疑嘅行為要自行申報<br />\n<br />\n利申：我自己係咁做"},{"pid":"540ab91a3064d0f0877eebdbaf5443aba036315d","tid":296460,"uid":80909,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"你個利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到你真係拍拖就明架喇<br />\n日日見住自己條女同唔同仔pm<br />\n乜都同人講但唔同你講 你會咁理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"06146417d3cc980ec4134c21cf4346b9cadd7ccf","tid":296460,"uid":22578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"晚晚skype個陣 佢同其他異性wts你又點睇<br />\n唔係話唔比同異性有接觸<br />\n但係可以避忌下囉"},{"pid":"990313900ec2092b567e4856f222eb0a397c2bfa","tid":296460,"uid":41737,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93872a69e4a4d4c4a47036a6e919915d47b0ed27","tid":296460,"uid":431,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"到你有拖拍你連老母都唔要啦垃圾毒撚"},{"pid":"b6b32f19627f503fae860860b609c39132e92952","tid":296460,"uid":4351,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"未撚拍過拖就收埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係字多就有道理㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   快啲做暑期作業"},{"pid":"9cefc538a5d437433a1b17dc5c46686cc94fb078","tid":296460,"uid":3688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"唔使斷晒<br />\n但係起碼要同異性保持距